1:14:45.773 --> 1:14:49.524
Oh yes, the face of the hammer.

1:14:49.526 --> 1:14:51.195
So this is the face,

1:14:52.154 --> 1:14:54.238
let's go a little deeper.

1:14:54.240 --> 1:14:55.989
