1:17:11.085 --> 1:17:12.417
Thomas, I'm gonna get the car
ready.

1:17:12.419 --> 1:17:15.128
Mom, can I just talk
to you for second please?

1:17:15.130 --> 1:17:17.339
I'm sorry I didn't tell
you that he was lying.

1:17:17.341 --> 1:17:18.924
You should have called us.

1:17:18.926 --> 1:17:19.925
We're in a rush, but listen.

1:17:19.927 --> 1:17:21.051
It could've been a trap,
instead you do this

1:17:21.053 --> 1:17:23.553
