mess again.

1:17:23.555 --> 1:17:24.429
I'm sorry, I didn't know.

1:17:24.431 --> 1:17:27.432
Look Ash, we have to do this
now.

1:17:27.434 --> 1:17:30.771
But if you want, we can talk
as soon as I come back, okay?

1:17:49.957 --> 1:17:52.124
You better not have any stupid
ideas

1:17:52.126 --> 1:17:54.042
going through your head.

1:17:54.044 --> 1:17:57.629
When we get outside, you
so much as look at someone

1:17:57.631 --> 1:17:59.965
the wrong way, I will slice your
ear,

1:17:59.967 --> 1:18:02.261
oh for fucks sake.

1:18:03.554 --> 1:18:06.473
